<h2 class="content-heading cufoned">&quot;Device&quot; - Desktop Style Premium Template</h2>
<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Device</strong> is a &quot;Desktop Style&quot; Ajax based animated website template, designed by the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.idangero.us" title="Premium Templates Scripts Graphics">iDangero.us</a> team. This template is perfect for small business websites, IT projects, or it can be used as a fashion site.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify">Page content is displayed in the windows that you can <strong>drag</strong>, <strong>resize</strong> and <strong>minimize</strong> (and later expand). You can put any content (flash, html, php, iframe etc.) inside the &quot;window&quot;. Due to the use of Ajax, your users do not need to wait the reloading of entire site. All content pages are loading &quot;on the fly&quot;.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify">Smooth and good looking animation and Ajax features of this template are realized with JavaScript jQuery and jQuery UI libraries.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify">Template does not have a typical site menu with a links. Instead menu, you can see grey rectangles in the center of home page and small square icons below. To open menu you need to click on middle rectangle on the background image.</p>
<p style="text-align:justify">Device comes with animated Slideshow section on the top. To open Slideshow you have to click on the left bottom rectangle on the background image. You can put any content (flash, html, php, iframe, etc) into the every slide.</p>
